name: Assik
description:
Sixth stop of my Interstellar Journey; For quite some time I've been looking for something that I feel passionate about, I recall reading about this human concept that they used to call 'music', and following patterns of the past, there should be a place based around this idea. Now that I'm here, a variety of sounds present in the background create a peaceful aura around the place, and the waves of these same sounds ripple across the massive body of water. I enjoy my time here.
